FBIS4-12219 "drnes067dd_94001" FBIS-NES-94-067 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 Palestinian Affairs Hamas Claims Responsibility for 'Afula Attack Hamas Claims Responsibility for 'Afula Attack TA0604151094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1400 GMT 6 Apr 94 TA0604151094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] has assumed responsibility for the 'Afula attack, claiming that its men perpetrated the attack. In a leaflet distributed in Janin, Hamas said that the name of the suicide terrorist is Ra'id Zakarnah, 19, of Qabatiyah. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that a short while ago, the security forces arrived in Qabatiyah, and took Zakarnah's father to the Ha'emeq Hospital to identify the body.
